---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About MyZip"
	description="What MyZip is and why we built it"
	pubDate={new Date('2026-06-15')}
>
	<p>
		MyZip is a hyper-local social timeline built for your neighborhood. Instead of an endless
		global feed, you get posts, questions, and updates from the people and places within your
		ZIP code — making it easier to stay connected to what's actually happening nearby.
	</p>

	<p>
		We started MyZip because local community information is scattered across dozens of apps,
		Facebook groups, and Nextdoor threads. We wanted a single, clean place where neighbors
		could share what matters to them — without the noise of the broader internet.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is where we share product updates, stories behind features, and lessons learned
		along the way. We're a small team building in public, and we'd love for you to follow along.
	</p>

	<p>
		Have feedback or want to get involved? Open an issue on{' '}
		<a href="https://github.com/CaptainLee2009/myzip-blog/issues">GitHub</a> — we're always listening.
	</p>
</Layout>
